<h2 id="10">3. Possible uses for coupons</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Coupons all have codes which belong to a campaign and which can either be redeemed once or multiple times. Coupons are redeemed during the order process. The discount value is displayed at this time. Coupons can be sent to customers as special offer codes within emails or gift cards can be sold as items in your online store. The buyer then receives the coupon code as a PDF document.</p>
