</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Select a variable for <a href="/en/crm/sending-emails"><strong>email templates</strong></a> (see below). The option <strong>No variable</strong> is selected by default. Once a variable has been selected, it can no longer be used for other campaigns.</p>
</div></div></td>
