<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="25">5.1. Example for calculating coupons for special offers and gift cards</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The <strong>Coupon variety</strong> is selected in the <strong>Coupon</strong> area within the <strong>Settings</strong> tab. The coupon value will be calculated differently depending on which coupon variety is selected. For example, <strong>coupons for special offers</strong> are calculated similarly to discounts.</p>
</div>
<div class="admonitionblock tip">
<table>
<tbody><tr>
<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-tip" title="Tip"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
