<h2 id="50">6. Searching for campaigns</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The <strong>Campaigns</strong> tab provides you with an overview of the most important information about existing campaigns.</p>
</div>
<table class="tableblock frame-all grid-all spread">
