<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="170">9.6. Displaying the coupon total on invoices</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Each coupon that is sold will be displayed as an individual stock unit on the invoice. In order for the total value of redeemed coupons to be displayed on the invoices, you need to take a look at the invoice’s layout and make sure that you entered text into the field name next to the words <strong><a href="/en/order-processing/orders/settings/documents#1">Coupon value (net)</a></strong>.</p>
</div>
